      summary: End Game
      operationId: endGame
      description: |
        The EndGame request is used whenever a round is over and there was no EndGame (true) parameter in either Debit or Credit.

        It is the explicit round-closure call when no separate credit is needed or when the vendor chooses to close the round separately.

        HTTP code of an error response should be 200.
